    label: 'Ease of Use',
    icon: '‚öôÔ∏è',
    description: 'One-hand folds, intuitive buckles, clear assembly instructions, adjustability, how quickly you can perform common tasks sleep-deprived at 3am.',
    color: 'bg-blue-50 border-blue-200 text-blue-700',
  },
  {
